{"id": "ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1543, "displayName": {"text": "Marufuku Ramen", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Contemporary spot for Japanese ramen (including hakata style), along with rice bowls, beer & sake.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OdE1EUldiamRRTm1Sb2VURlJPV2RZYVd4UlJVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Totally wanted to be impressed. Noodles were delicious, not gonna lie. They were a great tenderness and consistency. The broth was a lot less oily than I was expecting for a Hakata/Fukuoka style tonkotsu. I'm still trying to get used to canned corn kernels in ramen. I know people dig it. I'm just not there yet. Attentive staff. Coming from Hawaii/Japan, Marufuku was just ok for us.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Totally wanted to be impressed. Noodles were delicious, not gonna lie. They were a great tenderness and consistency. The broth was a lot less oily than I was expecting for a Hakata/Fukuoka style tonkotsu. I'm still trying to get used to canned corn kernels in ramen. I know people dig it. I'm just not there yet. Attentive staff. Coming from Hawaii/Japan, Marufuku was just ok for us.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107382728028057145303/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPZHmgyoY3dk2Y1QGJidfxZiw26BtZf9PBs8_iJOwhs1q6QA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-14T09:24:49.239339637Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OdE1EUldiamRRTm1Sb2VURlJPV2RZYVd4UlJVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OdE1EUldiamRRTm1Sb2VURlJPV2RZYVd4UlJVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857de19d3623a3:0xcaca2c218406acd5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMWVFNHlhVWhST1ZCSVJtTkxhRFZQVFhOVmRGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "My wife wanted to try this place as she's a big fan of ramen. We both got a bowl of the Hakata Tonkotsu DX. But not before starting with a few appetizers, like their Marufuku bites and classic Takoyaki.\nThe food was filling but I liked the appetizers more. I would try their curry next time.\nWe tried their hot sake but it wasn't a favorite. We would try their cold ones next time.\nStaff was very friendly and attentive. Kept our water glasses full and made us feel welcome.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My wife wanted to try this place as she's a big fan of ramen. We both got a bowl of the Hakata Tonkotsu DX. But not before starting with a few appetizers, like their Marufuku bites and classic Takoyaki.\nThe food was filling but I liked the appetizers more. I would try their curry next time.\nWe tried their hot sake but it wasn't a favorite. We would try their cold ones next time.\nStaff was very friendly and attentive. Kept our water glasses full and made us feel welcome.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Justin G.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113656428388950309477/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB0YqVafMeZS7l1JSCvBAfvV-01LTEkt0RkoTjnDQRftdD6rc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-07T22:34:19.807489531Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMWVFNHlhVWhST1ZCSVJtTkxhRFZQVFhOVmRGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMWVFNHlhVWhST1ZCSVJtTkxhRFZQVFhOVmRGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857de19d3623a3:0xcaca2c218406acd5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFZXWkdjbUZJVFhSWFZXTkNaV0o2VDJOWVJrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Bebelin was such a wonderful server. It was my first time eating at this establishment, and she gave our party the service experience of a lifetime. She was bubbly, kind, and made sure that we were taken care of throughout the duration of our stay. The food was delicious and offered in a beautiful ceramic bowl that highlighted their special attention to detail. The presentation, food quality, and waitstaff make me excited to dine here again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Bebelin was such a wonderful server. It was my first time eating at this establishment, and she gave our party the service experience of a lifetime. She was bubbly, kind, and made sure that we were taken care of throughout the duration of our stay. The food was delicious and offered in a beautiful ceramic bowl that highlighted their special attention to detail. The presentation, food quality, and waitstaff make me excited to dine here again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Juan Pablo De La Cruz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107109636852646920271/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEBVaDesSwdWk1G9gpLfablxd78GcsG5koRoBF7WcZ4CIZExdq=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-20T02:13:05.305388113Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFZXWkdjbUZJVFhSWFZXTkNaV0o2VDJOWVJrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFZXWkdjbUZJVFhSWFZXTkNaV0o2VDJOWVJrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857de19d3623a3:0xcaca2c218406acd5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVRtNDRXSFJGTkVkck5rUkNkSFkwVjJodFZXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This ramen place was on my list but always crowded and today I got to expect it. I didn't try anything other than the spicy tantan noodles but felt it was no more than a 4. The noodles were very tough, the broth tasted very powdery and the grounded chicken was a no-op.\n\nI also don't like how they don't have opinionated authentic vs spicy broths and offer any spice level with any broth. Tells me not proud of their work.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This ramen place was on my list but always crowded and today I got to expect it. I didn't try anything other than the spicy tantan noodles but felt it was no more than a 4. The noodles were very tough, the broth tasted very powdery and the grounded chicken was a no-op.\n\nI also don't like how they don't have opinionated authentic vs spicy broths and offer any spice level with any broth. Tells me not proud of their work.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Pramod", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113970417763766554324/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjuhteVdlKuGiw203xJsUZCoP50xD7Nf-QVt8ZmDO7gjK9WJf1VQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-08T06:37:59.261051770Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVRtNDRXSFJGTkVkck5rUkNkSFkwVjJodFZXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVRtNDRXSFJGTkVkck5rUkNkSFkwVjJodFZXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857de19d3623a3:0xcaca2c218406acd5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vNFdVWnJOV3A0VkV4bGREUkJURFpVUzI4d1VXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place was so so so good. There was definitely a bit of a wait, but once we got seated the service was incredibly fast. We ordered within minutes, and a few minutes later we were served all of our food. The food was amazing, the pork was so tender and the pork broth was so flavorful. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place was so so so good. There was definitely a bit of a wait, but once we got seated the service was incredibly fast. We ordered within minutes, and a few minutes later we were served all of our food. The food was amazing, the pork was so tender and the pork broth was so flavorful. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Maya Udkow", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114161401265202203951/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYOt_UpOkrLiXVK3fFGOlkqZn_d89Qk3FgB7wrdYT_5859b2obrw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-23T04:17:27.792099674Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vNFdVWnJOV3A0VkV4bGREUkJURFpVUzI4d1VXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vNFdVWnJOV3A0VkV4bGREUkJURFpVUzI4d1VXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857de19d3623a3:0xcaca2c218406acd5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJoyM2neF9hYAR1awGhCEsyso/photos/AWCwydidCL6H9fVb3uK0ip5jIH5G13htrNUcKZ0VBn4id1Z-d0i_v2CmIfr8oEc9oDcB5TLNrqmz5ZWqB6r_ulv4pKkcwMw0IECcKwrPHKaXsQGCZBOAFYg6Chmxtef98qN5eWOIy_IzdFgNm1uv6xKPGzhlTNU2lEkKdXy-Ur-bJGHgEHn89daAT4MVckRbuqW4LJJv6-y7e69XYx3AJvSU0wS06KXiahNq_2u11pV0lgLbfuDfi7Mlff4vbLKYCR5iok9Hsi_QYD4V0yhlyEOrvPuYb5XrikXYeYPp7a67PxNUFGx7h_gLAcjvM_kqKPsXhMnJZBXG49tN97QH2W70sa3kARt6u2BPLC_Tlwh2YUrLIHMkG9ehQs8JIaXwKO17jepUG3JcFDMMldIBLf-oyXn1pXzqSdUkVq89OvQLGOGImuit5NY0n8DbsxnVsdN6", "widthPx": 1494, "heightPx": 1014, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Lull Mengesha", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/104607344012722160405", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUcfn_5K9_b3gRdhpSmhCdfdQWr2sDQ4Q1cM-KZ5PQMYA0oX2I0w=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagConte